<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>١ -<span class="c5"> قَال الْبُخَارِيُّ ج٦ص١٦٧:</span> قَوْلُهُ تَعَالَى: <span class="c3">{وَيْلٌ لِلْمُطَفِّفِينَ}</span> <span class="c4">[المطففين: ١]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">المُطَفِّفُ:</span> لاَ يُوَفِّي غَيْرَهُ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>